name: 实时油价查询
desc: 通过网络API查询当前油价，默认查询地区为广东省，可修改脚本指定其它地区

tiles:
  - name: gas-price
    interval: 3600
    title: '实时油价信息'
    content: '刷新中...'
    icon: 'fuelpump.fill'
    backgroundColor: '#FB8C00'

script-providers:
  gas-price:
    url: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RS0485/network-rules/main/scripts/gas-price.js
    interval: 86400
